{"tid":2121361,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"個分入到U但中英文2左點算好？","createTime":"2020-07-23T09:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T11:31:10.000Z","uid":135445,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a1dce7996540ca7c0d008561fd76ce31bf028be3","tid":2121361,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"如果你係b5 2x分但中文2左<br />\n我會建議你考慮雙修asso<br />\n始終中文都係比較難控制到同冇咁易升grade既科(閱讀唔明就真係唔明<br />\nwriting一有離題就2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n同埋係風險分散角度<br />\n只係讀中文一科既話再炒左就蝕足一年<br />\n英文同理啦<br />\n<br />\n而如果你係b5 2x分但英文2左<br />\n我建議你真係雙修<br />\nasso/hd大把機會學到英文(上堂已經係用英文)<br />\n成年浸住英文底自然會好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比返少少stat大家<br />\n中英2上3個比例係2x%<br />\n雖然當中一定會有hea既人<br />\n但唔好覺得升grade係好容易既事(特別係2222-&gt;2既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n希望大家諗好度好先行動<br />\n話哂一年時間值至少十皮<br />\n有野想問/知歡迎comment<br />\n利申英文2上3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2017拎3323-&gt;2018拎3332"},{"pid":"64aaaf94003bfd7c290edde50e17f9a903c81175","tid":2121361,"uid":142872,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:08:45.000Z","msg":"即係個分入唔到u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ad0c472fa7eeaf0df386bb96fd2693f463d39a","tid":2121361,"uid":135445,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:10:44.000Z","msg":"同埋大家雙修如果想讀polyhd真係要諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然Gpa ~2.9/3就大機會入返Poly yr3 degree<br />\n但你yr1就已經讀緊degree year2野<br />\n(例如civil hd yr1要讀3大mechanics)<br />\n年中唔少人quit<br />\n利申讀過一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d9202dc056b6b9725404f05506c5be4e31bf59","tid":2121361,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0